{"tid":997714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏！孫楊保鑣用鐵槌打爛血液樣本 拒藥檢隨時終身停賽","createTime":"2019-01-27T11:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T02:23:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":479,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"d597cf0399c3d9f27966329747b9ec5fd43f78b0","tid":997714,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:33:34.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒周日報道，中國游泳選手孫楊在去年九月的一次藥檢中拒絕提供尿液樣本，他的保鑣更用鐵槌敲破血液樣本，世界反禁藥組織已經向國際體育仲裁法庭提告，孫楊隨時面臨終身停賽。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《星期日泰晤士報》周日的報道，世界反禁藥組織（WADA）去年九月四日曾經到孫楊位於浙江的家中進行突擊藥檢，不過孫楊當時並不在家，因此WADA人士等了一個小時。直至晚上11時孫楊回家後，一位護士向他抽血取樣，不過當WADA人員向孫楊要求尿液樣本時遭到拒絕。<br />\n孫楊當時表示WADA人員所出示的文件和證件不足以證明他們是獲WADA授權，因此拒絕合作。據報道指，當時孫楊的母親楊明亦在場，並向WADA人員聲稱自己與警察方面有關係，可以隨時叫警察來查證有關人員身份。<br />\n<br />\n報道指事件擾攘多個小時，及後在場的WADA人員致電瑞典總部要求指示時，電話的另一方傳出玻璃破碎的聲音。據報孫楊當時指示自己的保鑣用鐵槌破壞已經存封好的血液樣本，更把測試官的文件撕爛，事件最後到凌晨四時才平息。<br />\n國際泳聯在本月初就有關事件召開聽證會，不過結果就指出，WADA人員當時準備的文件並不充份，認為責任並不在孫楊一方。不過WADA在上訴期內決定向國際體育仲裁法庭提出上訴，報道指假如WADA上訴得直的話，孫楊隨時面臨終生停賽。現時WADA和國際泳聯都未有就事件作出回應。<br />\n而孫楊一方就透過北京藍鵬律師事務所發聲明，指《星期日泰晤士報》的報道不實，並提出三點藥檢程序問題，指當日包括血、尿檢驗官在內的三名工作人員無法提供IRTM公司對檢查手授權文件，亦無法提供反禁藥檢查官資格證明及護士執業證等，另外三人也在報告中作虛假陳述。聲明亦指，國際泳聯在去年11月19日在瑞士洛桑舉行13小時的聽證會，孫楊本人、其代表律師張起淮、IDTM公司的證人也接受詢問，其後今年1月3日，國際泳聯裁決孫楊沒有違反世界反禁藥條例，因此孫楊保留追究《星期日泰晤士報》的法律權利。"},{"pid":"86981d3ab944aa5a8ab99c3ca82b0a05ca9630fa","tid":997714,"uid":41404,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.smh.com.au/sport/swimming/hot-water-sun-yang-smashed-blood-test-with-hammer-20190127-p50tyd.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fsport%2Fswimming%2Fhot-water-sun-yang-smashed-blood-test-with-hammer-20190127-p50tyd.html&d=6cLUeJot05wT1KwRYHvTdv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=cc090afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smh.com.au/sport/swimming/hot-water-sun-yang-smashed-blood-test-with-hammer-20190127-p50tyd.html</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Sunday Times in London wrote that Sun and his team, including his mother Ming Yang, had concerns with the identification documents of testers and he and a security guard were alleged to have crushed a sealed vial with a hammer. If true, the incident could see the controversial swimmer facing a life ban from competition.<br />\n<br />\nSun already has a doping suspension to his name and was called out as a &lsquo;drug cheat&rsquo; by Horton in Rio three years ago. Horton was able to back up his words with a thrilling victory but he was the subject of relentless online attacks from Chinese swimming fans, to whom Sun is little short of an icon."},{"pid":"c0c142e17d596b4267131cd8635226c447cbd6cc","tid":997714,"uid":56999,"like":507,"dislike":2,"score":505,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qNruLg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qNruLg.jpg&h=f5900971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5tBRYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5tBRYB.jpg&h=b5427acf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a7a1b41903b7aa03864eac6a2faa3148e87f65c","tid":997714,"uid":11001,"like":423,"dislike":3,"score":420,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"尿紫楊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b88d135b5273ad11560ef410fe9c2dcc7c78f4e","tid":997714,"uid":35430,"like":267,"dislike":1,"score":266,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"向WADA人員聲稱自己與警察方面有關係，可以隨時叫警察來查證有關人員身份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將警民關係推向國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e70cf3f87c48a5b69be3bba5aa1c8b4e969c84","tid":997714,"uid":17646,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"屋企都要保鑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273f9f0352671eb515ab83c54106d54726802eea","tid":997714,"uid":122264,"like":85,"dislike":3,"score":82,"quote":{"pid":"75e70cf3f87c48a5b69be3bba5aa1c8b4e969c84","tid":997714,"uid"